The paper deals with logic programming transformations, type inference, and combinatorics of lambda terms, which are topics that are typically covered in the sub-categories of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), and Theoretical Computer Science (cs.TL).
